description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents SISTEMAS INESTABLES performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 12, 2024.

Songs:
Descenso
Retorno de Saturno
Motus

Javier Hechenleitner Thieck – Drums & Synthesizers
José Tomás Molina Galdames – Keyboard, Guitar, Drums & Synthesizers
Santiago Corvalán Garretón – Bass Guitar & Synthesizers

Host: Jewel Loree

Guest Audio Engineer: Jen Yovanolo 
Audio Mixer: José Tomás Molina
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Jonathan Jacobson, Luke Knecht & Scott Holpainen
